title: Please Don’t Show Your Son
author: 缘漫动漫-缘娘
synopsis:
缘漫动漫-缘娘 ini bercerita tentang
Lin Xiuyu, the Sea King, transmigrates into a world of supernatural abilities, where he can copy others’ abilities just by physical contact? That’s so impressive! From now on, he embarks on a journey of turning the tables by getting close to people… Wait, sister-in-law, don’t hit me! I’m not fooling around, I’m really doing something legitimate!
